{"tid":2490194,"cid":30,"subCid":0,"title":"3年幾感情話完就完，忘記唔到","createTime":"2021-04-15T11:52:04.000Z","updateTime":"2021-04-15T17:29:49.000Z","uid":53101,"like":14,"dislike":6,"uniUserReply":28,"replies":[{"pid":"8aa9d2416ed07d96c9b5550f7774cc0f97a980c3","tid":2490194,"uid":53101,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2021-04-15T11:52:04.000Z","msg":"一齊左3年幾 即使有嘈下交 每次都會一齊溝通解決到<br />\n過去3年充滿快樂回憶 當佢結婚對象 曾經想幫佢戴每條頸鏈 戒指<br />\n<br />\n無諗到無第三者干涉 安守本份 大家努力維繫愛情<br />\n最後都係抵受唔住現實殘酷 生活既無奈 因為意見分歧要分開<br />\n<br />\n呢兩晚 每日個腦海不斷諗起同佢晚往事 本以為自己係一個好理性既人 20幾年未喊過 ，每次諗起往事 眼淚就自動標出黎，重新認識咩叫傷心既感覺。 個心比人掏空果種感覺。<br />\n<br />\n日子都係要過，但真係好想每個節日都想同佢過。<br />\n<br />\n最後送上一首歌<br />\n<a href=\"https://youtu.be/IVKCHgf2ur4\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fyoutu.be%2FIVKCHgf2ur4&d=Uh5SjXth0XRRLWSKrhPNwM4e4tfxBia5339duguOAPM%3D&h=02d69599\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://youtu.be/IVKCHgf2ur4</a>"},{"pid":"e461d6f9ef0842d71ceb49506f8951b973044ec0","tid":2490194,"uid":63675,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-04-15T11:53:54.000Z","msg":"咩2見"},{"pid":"7c1349ce9e0aa5fd22b3fbce3a4d7fbb86d7be58","tid":2490194,"uid":154406,"like":15,"dislike":11,"score":4,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-04-15T11:54:46.000Z","msg":"哈 又一pair分手 開心～"},{"pid":"ee6f3edc7413aff6cd48dff6a916327fcf0d8291","tid":2490194,"uid":162539,"like":22,"dislike":0,"score":22,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2021-04-15T11:55:30.000Z","msg":"觀察多排先話無第三者啦"},{"pid":"b9a3cd701e924224338ccd6fbf3b668c0724c50a","tid":2490194,"uid":118490,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2021-04-15T11:55:32.000Z","msg":"今次衰咩？"},{"pid":"943605823ec6b9a7b97f1a3b6a9e49d40898d42c","tid":2490194,"uid":279927,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-04-15T11:56:50.000Z","msg":"人生無常， 面對現實<br />\n我都走唔出困境"},{"pid":"fffe40fea95916c945342c372afec77aa618b26b","tid":2490194,"uid":104232,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"ee6f3edc7413aff6cd48dff6a916327fcf0d8291","tid"